Description: RDF version of the Apertium bilingual dictionary PT-GL. The original dataset (in LMF) comes from http://hdl.handle.net/10230/17115 . The RDF version of the lexica is modelled using lemon (http://lemon-model.net/) and the translation module (http://purl.org/net/translation). More about the Apertium RDF dictionaries at http://linguistic.linkeddata.es/apertium/
Languages: en; es; de; fr; it; la; ca; sv; se; gl; pt; ro; oc; eu; ast; an; eo
